<div class="zm-item-answer-detail">
<div class="zm-item-answer-author-info">
<h3 class="zm-item-answer-author-wrap">


<a data-tip="p$t$blahblahlol" href="/people/blahblahlol">付恒</a>，<strong title="最好的学习方法就是将其重新实现。" class="zu-question-my-bio">最好的学习方法就是将其重新实现。</strong>

</h3>
<a href="javascript:;" name="collapse" class="collapse meta-item zg-right"><i class="z-icon-fold"></i>收起</a>
</div>
<div class="zm-item-vote-info " data-votecount="1">

<span class="voters">
<span class="user-block"><a data-tip="p$t$yu-xiao-mao-30" href="http://www.zhihu.com/people/yu-xiao-mao-30" class="zg-link" title="余小猫">余小猫</a></span>
</span>


<span>赞同</span>


</div>
<div class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="1035189" data-action="/answer/content">

<div class="fixed-summary zm-editable-content clearfix">去写吧。你一天写5000字，写一个月，就是一本15万字的小说了，不管写的多烂，至少你可以在别人面前吹牛，说自己是个小说家了。只要1个月而已哦。<br><br>我就不多说了，看下这个视频吧：<br><a href="http://v.163.com/movie/2012/1/F/F/M8LD0V9UJ_M8LV25RFF.html" class=" wrap external" target="_blank" rel="nofollow noreferrer">超短集_马特・卡茨:尝试做新事情30天<i class="icon-external"></i></a>


</div>

</div>
</div>
</div>
